    <body>           
        <%- include('./partials/header', {home: 'active', color: color})%>
        <div id="about-logo" class="vcenter">
            <!--<img class="noselect" src="./imgs/hi.png">-->
            <h1 class="noselect" style="color: white; font-size: 15.5vw;">hi</h1>
        </div>
        <div id="about">
            <p>
                <strong>What is hi?</strong>
                <br/>
                hi is a giveaway Discord Guild/Website where free stuff is given away.
                <br/>
                <strong>What kind of free stuff?</strong>
                <br/>
                Steam games, Amazon gift cards, PayPal cash, Google Play Store gift cards, iTunes gift cards, and sooooooo much more.
                <br/>
                <strong>Why do you give away "free stuff"? What's the catch?</strong> 
                <br/>
                The catch is that you have to be social, and participate in our community discussions (yes, that's right, we're a social server too).
                <br/>
                We do not display ads on any of our pages, sell your data in any way (we don't even collect your data), or mine any cryptocurrency on your computer.
                <br/>
                <strong>Why do you need both the website and Discord?</strong>
                <br/>
                We have way more control over giveaways when using a website we made. We use Discord as it allows for easily communicating with other people.
                <br/>
                Our main goal is just to have large Discord server where people just be social (sometimes it is all about the numbers).
                <br />
                <strong>You don't have a "contact us" section on this website. How do I contact you?</strong>
                <br />
                You can contact us by joining hi or DMing us on Discord (FrostTaco#2938 and LittleWhole#1337).
                <br />
                <h1>Ready to join hi?</h1>
                <br/>
                <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://discord.gg/Xda3AVn" role=button id="big-join-hi-button">Join hi!</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <footer class="bg-<%= color %>">
            <%- include('./partials/footer'); %>
        </footer>
        <div id="cookienotif" class="vcenter cookies bg-<%= color %>">
            <%- include('./partials/cookies'); %>
        </div>
    </body>
